<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued May 09 at 1:44AM MDT until May 09 at 12:00PM MDT by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON MDT TODAY...
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations up to 3 inches.
* WHERE...Fergus County.
* WHEN...Until Noon MDT today.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the Monday morning commute.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling. The latest road
conditions can be obtained by calling 5 1 1 or visiting the MDT Road
Report website.</instruction>
